des:
ABC Song has multiple tracks of the classic children's alphabet ABC song.

Just say to your Echo, "open ABC Song" to hear a new version of the song.

The songs are in random order. Play therm as many times as you like for free!

Sing along and help your child learn the alphabet, right on your echo!
